<p corresp='TTP25086201P2' xml:id='OTP25086201P2'>At the meeting of the citizens of Enterprise Called by the <rs ref='#S63935'>Mayor</rs> for the purpose of raising money for the <rs ref='#S51788'>Vicksburg</rs> Sufferers the following <rs ref='#S95150'>amounts</rs> were subscribed &amp; paid to wit.
